infra/terraform.tfstate.backup
infra/tfplan
infra/~/
**/*.tfstate
**/*.tfstate.*
**/*.tfvars
!**/*.tfvars.example
**/.terraform/

# Frontend
frontend/node_modules/
frontend/.next/

